Package: spatialwarningsGis
Type: Package
Title: Spatial Early Warning Signals of Ecosystem Degradation - GIS extensions
Version: 2.0.0
Author: Alexandre Genin
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Maintainer: Alexandre Genin <alexandre.genin@umontpellier.fr>
Description: Tools to compute and assess significance of early-warnings signals (EWS) of ecosystem degradation on raster data sets. This package includes extensions to apply the package spatialwarnings on GIS-related objects (Genin et al. (2018) <doi:10.1111/2041-210X.13058>).
URL: https://github.com/spatial-ews/spatialwarningsGis
Depends: R (>= 3.3.0), spatialwarnings
LazyData: true
